We initially removed horizontal swiping between your positions and watchlist. A lot of you didn’t really like that.

So now, much like Backstreet, horizontal swiping is back! Swipe back and forth to your heart’s content.

Bug fixes:
- Fixed an issue around collection tags, so browsing collections is a little easier now.
- Fixed an issue around Robinhood Gold calculations.
